{"tid":1026674,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日去地鐵客服中心，有條阿嬸插隊","createTime":"2019-02-18T09:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T10:54:42.000Z","uid":208140,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"739ce03cfedbc7910bc6f976794e92e82b61e340","tid":1026674,"uid":208140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:43:22.000Z","msg":"今日去地鐵客務中心搞張私人八達通，因為要退錢、簽名、比錢，所以都需要2-3分鐘時間。<br />\n點知有個阿嬸企我後邊，一直重複講：「嘩乜依啲時間先搞啲咁嘅嘢呀，我趕時間架，搞咁耐，搞成2分鐘。」<br />\n跟住無啦啦走咗上來插隊，拎住張100蚊同地鐵職員講要增值50蚊。講真嗰陣係非繁忙時間，你去7仔入完錢先入閘唔得？當你入咗閘先記得要增值，你唔識排隊？你唔識落車之後先去增值？仲要嘈嘈閉？係咪趕時間大曬？得你一個趕時間？"},{"pid":"cbd2cb6f26a618c3aacc7cb3081d257e1ca9648a","tid":1026674,"uid":186844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:44:33.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c844c5ad3ef4bc6a10fdde93ceb6736b4d1a17","tid":1026674,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:44:38.000Z","msg":"當時唔同佢嘈 而家上黎嘈有咩用？"},{"pid":"42063c74164316374e1f95906d5c339c7216c6ea","tid":1026674,"uid":18040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:44:41.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇當場屌佢呀"},{"pid":"6e17b08c3c8347de1c6ffed16e77d8f7f490935a","tid":1026674,"uid":20066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:46:04.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇咁鬧佢？<br />\n定得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 呢d畜生唔屌唔化<br />\n上次去海洋公園大大聲屌個2個呀嬸<br />\n仲補多句操你媽b驚佢聽唔明屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e487be1ad0dc3d8805e9892b457c13f817db36c","tid":1026674,"uid":39320,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hksan.net/forum/uploads/post-13-1262490750.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksan.net%2Fforum%2Fuploads%2Fpost-13-1262490750.jpg&h=d60cbb94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d407ef57c03d89c0ffeb4fe8cfb87ea7377fc5aa"